## Case Conventions Summary

| Item | Convention | Example |
|------|-----------|---------|
| Feature folders | kebab-case with prefix | `user-table-components/` |
| File names | kebab-case with prefix | `user-table-header.tsx` |
| Components | PascalCase | `UserTableHeader` |
| Functions | camelCase | `getUserTableData()` |
| Hooks | camelCase with `use` prefix | `useUserTable()` |
| Types | PascalCase with `T` prefix | `TUserTableProps` |
| Interfaces | PascalCase with `I` prefix | `IUserTableRepository` |
| Constants | SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE | `USER_TABLE_PAGE_SIZE` |
| Main feature folder | kebab-case (no prefix) | `user-table/` |

